author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Yeah, I know the thumbnail has almost nothing to do with the subject matter tonight, but who cares? I thought it would brighten up everyone's almost-Halloween. Join me, The Longman, Chris Gore, Movie Cynic and Despot as we get Stuckmanised hard, take a look at the growing backlash against the Witcher Season 4, and the news that Disney is officially pulling out of Doctor Who. 

Subscribe to Chris Gore: https://www.youtube.com/@FilmThreat
Subscribe to Cynic: https://www.youtube.com/@TheMovieCynic
Subscribe to Despot: https://www.youtube.com/@DespotofAntrim
title: Open Bar #162 - Witcher Backlash, Shelby Oaks, Frankenstein, RIP Doctor Who
